                            <td align="left" valign="top" class="Year1 border_top_left">
                                <p align="justify">The FARE charges was 1-ANNA (6 paise) per mile.But later on it was converted into Rupees and kilometers in the year 1959.TEA ALLOWANCE of 2- ANNAs i.e. (12paise) paid to the staff. </p>
                            </td>
