                            <tr>
                                <td align="left" valign="top" class="Year1 border_left">PMPML have its <strong>Managing&nbsp; Director</strong>, who is an<strong> IAS officer</strong> and Board of  Directors. The management consist the main officers : 
                 
                  <br>
                                    <strong><em>a</em></strong><strong><em>) </em></strong><strong><em>Joint Managing Director</em></strong><br>
                                    <strong><em>b</em></strong><strong><em>)</em></strong><strong><em> Chief Executive Officer</em></strong><br>
                                    <strong><em>c</em></strong><strong><em>)</em></strong><strong><em> Chief Engineer</em></strong><br>
                                    <strong><em>d) Finance  Manager</em></strong><br>
                                    <strong><em>e) Civil  Engineer</em></strong><br>
                                    <strong><em>f) Controllers  of Stores</em></strong><br>
                                    <strong><em>g) Administrative  Officer</em></strong><br>
                                    <strong><em>h) Labour &amp;  Public Relation officer</em></strong></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td align="left" valign="top" class="Year1 border_left">
                                    <div align="justify">The Pune Municipal Transport Committee has been formed in accordance to  the Bombay Provincial Municipal Corporations Act, 1949 (BPMC). The  PMPML is run as per the provisions in this Act. The operational system  of PMPML consists of 3 basic components:</div>
                                </td>
